Goodday how are you? I am new to advertising and your network. I have a pending advert and i am not sure if all is well set. Kindly check and advise.

Hi Tinashe! I'm doing well, thank you. I'd be happy to help you with your pending advert. Since you're new to advertising on our network, it's possible that your account hasn't been verified yet. To proceed with the verification process and have your account approved, please provide the following details by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification –
- Company's full address
- Company's legal entity name
- Company's EHID or DUNS number
- Primary contact person's name
- Company's phone number
Once we receive this information, we will conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status. We appreciate your cooperation in maintaining a secure and compliant advertising environment for all our partners.
Hie, ok thanx. If its an individual freelancer what do you require

Hi Tinashe! If you're an individual freelancer, you can still proceed with the verification process. Please provide the following details by emailing adsupport@newsbreak.com with the subject line: Business Verification –
- Your full address
- Your legal name
- Any relevant identification number (such as a tax ID or business registration number)
- Primary contact person's name (which would be your name)
- Your phone number
Once we receive this information, we will conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status. We appreciate your cooperation in maintaining a secure and compliant advertising environment for all our partners.
Ok thank you, let me do that.
You're welcome, Tinashe! If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out. Good luck with your advertising!
How long will the verification process take?

The verification process typically takes 2-3 days once we receive all the required information. Our team will review your details and update you on your account status as soon as possible. If you have any urgent concerns, feel free to reach out to adsupport@newsbreak.com.
You're welcome, Tinashe! If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
